Author: bleepbloophumanoid
Text: Please go to the ER. Anorexia has an extremely high mortality rate. Don’t let this disorder rob you of your life here on earth. I wish you the best ❤️

Author: bestrongandfast
Text: Please please go to the hospital, if you’re retaining that much fluid and not peeing it’s a medical emergency!! You might start to have trouble breathing too. Kidney problems can become heart, lung, brain, and eye problems. please get help! Stay safe ❤️❤️❤️
